    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/9004e8b8f1099de09b5cda077b179ca0.avif?t=1772042104\" width=573 height=103 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/853c55eeeb4b40e6335a150787f2e6dd.poster.avif?t=1772042104\" width=1170 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/853c55eeeb4b40e6335a150787f2e6dd.webm?t=1772042104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/853c55eeeb4b40e6335a150787f2e6dd.mp4?t=1772042104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">装满弹药，毒液突击队员们！组建 4 人小队，将淤泥之神及其不死军团打回地狱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/7d309e09756ff47bd15c76775c8f98c1.avif?t=1772042104\" width=442 height=121 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/d00df066b1ff069b51b8281d584da03a.poster.avif?t=1772042104\" width=1170 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/d00df066b1ff069b51b8281d584da03a.webm?t=1772042104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/d00df066b1ff069b51b8281d584da03a.mp4?t=1772042104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">组建 4 人小队，或在线加入其他突击队员，开启纯粹的合作混乱战局。复活倒下的队友、共享弹药、互相掩护，在疯狂激战中笑傲疆场。当感染者从四面八方蜂拥而至，团队协作不再是选择，而是生存的必需！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/ba1026646ef248d32a4499eec7586423.avif?t=1772042104\" width=419 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/d6edf9689194704bccacedcd8b45dc99.poster.avif?t=1772042104\" width=1170 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/d6edf9689194704bccacedcd8b45dc99.webm?t=1772042104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/d6edf9689194704bccacedcd8b45dc99.mp4?t=1772042104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">数千名感染者汹涌来袭、攻势如潮，拿起枪械、手榴弹和毁灭性技能，尽情宣泄怒火！借助 Saber 的 Swarm Engine (《World War Z》《Warhammer 40,000: 星际战士2》同款)，尸潮永不停歇，同时你手中的扳机也绝不能停！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/680e2c6882eaa6dd242a32262663665c.avif?t=1772042104\" width=287 height=121 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/2d1b9810c584b9820ed554e37fffb054.poster.avif?t=1772042104\" width=1170 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/2d1b9810c584b9820ed554e37fffb054.webm?t=1772042104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157830/extras/2d1b9810c584b9820ed554e37fffb054.mp4?t=1772042104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在半开放地图中搜寻散落的载具，在废土上疾驰狂飙。每款座驾都独具特色：有些搭载了强大火力或特殊技能，有些则配备了绞盘等实用工具。找到适合小队的载具，猛踩油门冲过尸潮，感受纯粹的力量与快感，没有什么比把僵尸碾成肉饼更过瘾的了！</p>",
